From the Infowars web site ::

On the Wednesday edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks with the founder, main songwriter, guitarist, and lead vocalist for the heavy metal band Megadeth, Dave Mustaine. 

He also talks with former Minnesota governor, Navy SEAL veteran, and television and radio host Jesse Ventura, who will break news on today's show. 

Alex breaks down the Greek economic implosion and the possibility the Mediterranean nation will hold a referendum and may not pay the debt it is claimed they owe to international bankers.
